OL,7,G1400 This Farming Life
OL,8,     F4/12. John and Antoinette have
OL,9,     Ftheir hands full, as Ben's had to
OL,10,     Ftake a full-time job. The Morrises
OL,11,     Fhave a very difficult lambing, and
OL,12,     FSally gets some long-awaited news.
OL,13,G1500 Landward
OL,14,     F11/26. Dougie is on Montrose Beach
OL,15,     Fmeasuring the increasing rate of
OL,16,     Fcoastal erosion.
OL,17,G1530 Beechgrove Garden
OL,18,     F11/26. George Anderson and Ruth
OL,19,     FVichos are back in the Beechgrove
OL,20,     FGarden just outside Aberdeen,
OL,21,     Fwhere the climate has been very
OL,22,     Fmixed over the last few weeks.
